(firstQuint)HDL Acute Lipid Optimization in Homozygous Familial Hypercholesterolemia.

 The PDS-2 cent System is intended to reduce coronary atheroma in patients with Homozygous Familial Hypercholesterolemia (HoFH).

 Subjects will receive serial infusions of autologous selectively delipidated HDL/pre enriched plasma following use of HDL Therapeutics' PDS-2 System.

